MERCURIES LIFE said unconsolidated sales
in November fell 39.67% to NT$5,005,049,000 from NT$8,296,094,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  11/2011          11/2010
Sales           5,005,049        8,296,094   
YOY%             -39.67%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           91,412,452      102,177,972  
YOY%             -10.54% 
=================================================================
 